data.description: Extremely rare end unit offering complete privacy in this pristine upscale condo in Fairhope. It has been meticulously upgraded and maintained, with a very open floor plan.  Currently the 3rd bedroom has been converted to a beautiful den but could easily be changed. Plantation shutters throughout. Crown molding in many areas. There is a large built-in hutch adjacent to kitchen, great for storage. New stove in 2023, new microwave in 2022. There is granite in the kitchen and both bathrooms.  Internal sprinkler system (allows for lower insurance). All flooring is either beautiful wood laminate or tile.  Exclusions include: all hanging draperies, free-standing book cabinet in library/den and dryer in laundry room, all exterior furniture on front porch, back screened porch and back patio.
